{
  "stem": "6803.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And on top was a little store, was a little sign up there, Gluck, like my name.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I says to the man there, my name is also Gluck.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe you can help me with a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN] They started to curse them, like [SPEAKING GERMAN] and you have a nerve.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I walked-- I marched--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In that town, yes, in that town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we walked by, and I-- we got to the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they put us in a room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gunskirchen.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gunskirchen.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the plan, to take us in that camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was out of everywhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was in a-- in a-- in a-- in the woods somewhere, and the barracks were made just [? slotting. ?] The plan was that to kill us all there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the way I heard after the war, that the Americans find out what they had then planned to do with these few people there in Gunskirchen.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they gave them an order, and each man we're going to find a dead man in that camp, there will be two Germans killed for that.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they stopped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they stopped killing us, but they didn't feed us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then two or three days, we start-- we got-- we started to get a package from the, uh, Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not liberated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were still under the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Three or four days before the liberation, we got from the Red Cross somehow some little packages.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was beans, not cooked, flour, not cooked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they gave us a little package, which wasn't enough even for one person, for 28 people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to divide between us. 28 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- I still remember that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Still there.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember there was a young boy.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
